{"tid":1861402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新世界旗下地盤因應疫情即日起停工兩星期","createTime":"2020-02-04T06:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T11:29:38.000Z","uid":51271,"like":191,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"f546831bc93ebaff91c3050edf2dacf3db05c4b5","tid":1861402,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"新世界發展旗下地盤因應疫情暫時停工。<br />\n<br />\n集團旗下建築公司向各承判商發通告指，因應疫情及確診本土傳染個案出現，決定所有地盤今日起關閉兩星期，至本月17日。<br />\n<br />\n通告又指會每周檢討復工日期。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，今次決定是因應員工及社區衛生而作此作出相關決定。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506552-20200204.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506552-20200204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=b96a0ddd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506552-20200204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8c8e8aeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506552-20200204.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"49acb0814609dc4587a91ec596f3314f76510ab7","tid":1861402,"uid":51271,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"新世界都怕地盤果d住支那既腥港人奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded05341d5cd51c241e6781b78f044c2fdf0e537","tid":1861402,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1154aad0d3fb33bb37edece7d3506682c0a7a5da","tid":1861402,"uid":71620,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202